divs: Sighting DetailsI were near enbankment near river Sava and photographing a test car, Ford Ranger. During the afternoon after finished photographing, I check a photos and seen an unidentified object on two of them. On first you can see a side of object and on second object is little bigger and looks as it flying towards me slightly tilted.
Summary: During photographing on river Sava in zagreb I catch a unidentified object with my camera, Nikon D300
